        <div id="block-block-3" class="block block-block">
                    <div class="content">
            <div style="margin-bottom: -40px;"><img style="border:none; background: none; float: right; padding: none; margin: none;" title="Fab" src="/files/fab.png" /><strong>Fabian Scherschel</strong> is a university student from Bonn, Germany working part-time as tech support for a large ISP. He is involved in the Fedora Design Team and dabbles in coding free software whenever he has some free time, which isn't often.<br/><br/>
<p><img style="border:none; background: none; float:right; padding: none; margin: none;" title="Dan" src="/files/dan.png" /><strong>Dan Lynch</strong> is a programmer, web developer and musician from Merseyside, UK. He used to work as a .NET developer before becoming an open source enthusiast and never looking back. Dan is often distro hopping and writing reviews of the coolest new technology whenever he gets a chance.</p></br/></br/></div>
